### AppBase Database API – Manual test requests
### Use with VS Code REST Client (humao.rest-client) or JetBrains HTTP Client
###
### Workflow:
### 1. Register/Login in auth.http → copy accessToken
### 2. Set @accessToken below
### 3. Run "Create – success" → copy "id" from response.data
### 4. Set @recordId below with that id
### 5. Run Get, Put, Delete (they use @recordId)

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@apiKey = hs_live_mnlIKCBxPqvSGZLcDsNqAstnMihqTQwVAcwJESDFLxpgpBuxrvWzQBkpSjJkQVwl
@accessToken = eyJhbGciOiJFZERTQSIsImtpZCI6IkM1aktPd1VrUGZZOGpPQWJnRWFLQVo5eGhDRGNCNWw1In0.eyJpYXQiOjE3NzQxOTc5OTUsInN1YiI6IjRVQm52M0gxVDA4b01ybXFmMXlFSWd4RWJ1TDBzbWFiIiwiZW1haWwiOiJtYW51YWwtdGVzdEBleGFtcGxlLmNvbSIsImFwcElkIjpudWxsLCJtZXRhZGF0YSI6Int9IiwiZXhwIjoxNzc0MTk4ODk1LCJpc3MiOiJodHRwOi8vbG9jYWxob3N0OjgwMDAiLCJhdWQiOiJodHRwOi8vbG9jYWxob3N0OjgwMDAifQ.sHnOaiFOxUZ0Chw4CAFNI1Q1uPhRUTyPZet7axgKlWABtwFVYLFytmUWQ7VmHr7sUAa06iAgvW1oPiYfceCwBQ
